In this video, we’ll show you the ongoing evolution of Google Container Registry into Artifact Registry. Specifically,  we’ll show you the new features that come with Artifact Registry - such as regional repositories, multiple repositories per project, and repository-native identity access management - and how artifact registry is able to integrate with Java and Cloud Build alike. 

Artifact Registry → https://goo.gle/3e4uLiw 


