It is best practice for businesses to continuously replicate operational data so they can make timely, data-driven business decisions. In this video, we’ll demo how you can easily replicate data in realtime from an Oracle database into BigQuery. We’ll show you how you can do this using Cloud Data Fusion’s replication accelerator that is integrated with Datastream. 

